{"comments":"Hue - position on the color wheel.\n\nMeasured in degrees from 0 to 359:\n- **0°/360°**: Red\n- **60°**: Yellow  \n- **120°**: Green\n- **180°**: Cyan\n- **240°**: Blue\n- **300°**: Magenta\n\nHue is cyclic - values outside 0-359 wrap around.\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Hue"],"Hue"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[102,32],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Hue.purs","start":[102,1]},"title":"eqHue"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Hue"],"Hue"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[103,34],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Hue.purs","start":[103,1]},"title":"ordHue"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Hue"],"Hue"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[106,31],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Hue.purs","start":[105,1]},"title":"showHue"}],"comments":"Hue value in degrees (0-359)\n\nRepresents position on the color wheel. Red at 0°, cycling through\nyellow, green, cyan, blue, magenta, and back to red at 360°.\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[100,22],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Hue.purs","start":[100,1]},"title":"Hue"},{"children":[],"comments":"Create a hue, clamping to 0-359\n","info":{"de